{"title":"DRIPCULT CERTIFIED HEAT","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"unholy-saint","title":"UNHOLY SAINT ♡","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32  WEARING M HOODIE.\r\n\r\n420 GSM\r\nPIPING WORK OVER SHOULDER, ARMS AND WAIST AREA\r\nPREMIUM 100% COTTON MATERIAL\r\nEMBROIDERY PRINT FRONT AND BACK (78,000+ embroidery stitches)\r\nBAGGY FIT [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS].\r\nCOMBED AND BIOWASHED.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStep into elevated streetwear with this 420 GSM super-premium sweatshirt, crafted for comfort, durability, and bold style. Made using combed and bio-washed fabric, it delivers a smooth, soft feel with long-lasting quality. The design features sleek piping work running across the shoulders, arms, and waist, adding a sharp, structured look. Front and back high-density embroidery make a strong statement, showcasing intricate detailing that stands out. With its relaxed fit, this sweatshirt blends effortless vibe with premium construction—perfect for everyday wear or standout street style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Machine wash the sweatshirt inside out with like colors.\r\n* Use cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\n* Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\n* Store the sweatshirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Sweatshirt with 420 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\n* Baggy fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\n* Unisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\n* Front pouch pocket for convenient storage and added warmth.\r\n* Soft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\r\n* Long sleeves and ribbed cuffs and hem provide a snug and stylish fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853858197658,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853858230426,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853858263194,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853858295962,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853858328730,"sku":"HOODIES(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2409.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/B6CFEE9B-C671-41C1-9335-0E6FB2AFEC1D.png?v=1769958160"},{"product_id":"midnight-drip","title":"MIDNIGHT DRIP","description":"\u003cp\u003e 420 GSM\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e HIGH-DENSITY “DRIP STUDIOS PROPERTY” FRONT PRINT\u003cbr\u003e TWO-WAY YKK ZIPPER CLOSURE\u003cbr\u003e BROAD STRUCTURED HOOD WITH KANGAROO POCKETS\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eUltra-heavy 420 GSM cotton fleece delivers exceptional weight, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTwo-way YKK zipper offers enhanced versatility, functionality, and long-lasting performance.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHigh-density “DRIP STUDIOS PROPERTY” print adds a bold yet refined visual statement.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBroad, structured hood creates an elevated and confident silhouette.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional kangaroo pockets provide everyday utility and warmth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePremium construction focused on comfort, structure, and longevity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft hand feel with breathable jersey backing for all-day wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDesigned as a statement essential that blends craftsmanship with attitude.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBaggy fit for relaxed, comfortable, and versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFront pouch pocket for added warmth and convenience.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eLong sleeves with ribbed cuffs and hem for a secure, structured fit.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881406779546,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881406812314,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881406845082,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881406877850,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881406910618,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881406943386,"sku":"HOODIES","price":2399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/AEFD019A-E6CF-4B7A-9207-4B466ABCC608.png?v=1769957835"},{"product_id":"certified-lover-ltd-ed","title":"CERTIFIED LOVER","description":"\r\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\r\nEmbroidery work front\/back.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM black oversized T-shirt is crafted to offer a bold, streetwear-inspired aesthetic with premium details. Designed with a white cloth lining running from top to bottom, as well as from the front neck to the shoulder area, it brings a fresh touch to your look. The front features an embroidered logo, adding a touch of sophistication and an elevated vibe to the piece. On the back, the embroidered “Certified Lover” (that too in embroidery) print adds an extra layer of exclusivity. Perfect for those who appreciate luxury and street style, this T-shirt combines comfort, durability, and high-end craftsmanship.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407434906,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407467674,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407500442,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407533210,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881407598746,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407631514,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00022copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440426"},{"product_id":"code-9-flagged","title":"CODE-9 FLAGGED","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Fabric with Raglan Sleeves. Front \u0026amp; Back Print. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 260 GSM T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who like their style bold and unapologetic. Featuring classic raglan sleeves, it delivers enhanced comfort, mobility, and a distinct athletic-inspired silhouette. The front showcases the Drip Studios brand print with a clean, confident presence, while the back makes a powerful statement with the phrase “Are You Flagged and Certified Lover.” Crafted from high-quality French terry cotton, this tee offers durability, breathability, and all-day comfort. CODE 9 is made for individuals who wear their mindset as confidently as their style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and print longevity. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM fabric for a structured, premium feel. Raglan sleeves for improved comfort and a relaxed yet refined fit. Boxy, oversized silhouette suitable for both men and women. Unisex design crafted to complement diverse body types. Soft, breathable French terry cotton ensures lasting comfort and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407664282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407697050,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407729818,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407795354,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407828122,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00076copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440450"},{"product_id":"holy-flex","title":"HOLY FLEX","description":"\u003cp\u003eMALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M TEE.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e280 GSM premium French terry fabric for a substantial and durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit with full raglan sleeves for relaxed comfort and easy movement.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClassic black and white color blocking with a crisp white body and deep black sleeves.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLow-density front print featuring subtle script “Drip Studios” branding.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVertical “Drip Studios” screen print on sleeves for a bold yet minimal look.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImpactful Christ face graphic on the back with low-density print for a softer, artistic texture.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePiping work over the armhole area enhances structure and detailing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed finish for smooth texture and long-lasting quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the tee inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or fabric damage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCore Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTee with 280 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a premium, substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOversized fit suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex article designed for versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable fabric ensures all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885005820058,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885005852826,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885005885594,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885005918362,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885005951130,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885005983898,"sku":"Reign1","price":1869.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00348copy_11zon_1.jpg?v=1771440511"},{"product_id":"ash-mode","title":"ASH MODE","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e MELANGE GREY WITH EMBROIDERY DETAIL\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e BELT LOOP FOR KEYS OR LIGHTER\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eConstructed from 420 GSM premium cotton fleece for superior structure, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eMelange grey color with signature Drip Studios embroidery detailing for subtle luxury.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSleek ankle zip allows adjustable styling and adds a refined touch.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDiscreet belt loop enhances practicality — ideal for holding keys, a lighter, or small essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette designed for relaxed comfort and versatile streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHeavyweight fabric ensures premium feel without compromising flexibility or movement.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePerfect blend of elevated minimalism and streetwear utility for everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e 