sity front and back prints for a bold, textured finish\r\n\r\nStatement graphics: \"FEAR NO ONE\" (front) \/ \"AGAINST ALL ODDS\" (back)\r\n\r\nWear it with confidence. Stand for something.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"L","offer_id":46885164712090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885164744858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885164777626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46885164843162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885164875930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885164908698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00177copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440486"},{"product_id":"ocean-phase","title":"OCEAN PHASE","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e NAVY BLUE WITH HIGH-DENSITY PRINT ON FRONT \u0026amp; EMBROIDERY NEAR ANKLE ZIP\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e BELT LOOP FOR KEYS OR LIGHTER\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium cotton fleece for a perfect balance of softness, structure, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBold DRIP STUDIOS high-density graphic print on the front adds statement-driven style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eEmbroidery detail near the ankle zipper enhances premium craftsmanship.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSmall ankle zipper allows adjustable styling and effortless fit over sneakers.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional belt loop provides utility for holding keys, a lighter, or small essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette designed for relaxed comfort and versatile streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHeavyweight fabric ensures warmth, durability, and elevated street-lux appeal.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885165990042,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885166022810,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885166055578,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885166088346,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885166121114,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885166153882,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/4181CC80-5506-4012-9AF8-9C03EC705494.png?v=1771567730"},{"product_id":"resilient","title":"RESILIENCE","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Boxy-Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Piping Work \u0026amp; Embroidery.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM boxy-fit T-shirt is designed for a strong, confident everyday statement with premium comfort at its core. Crafted from 100% French terry cotton, it offers a soft yet substantial feel with excellent breathability and durability. The design is elevated with refined piping work across the shoulders and front, adding depth and structure to the silhouette. Premium embroidery detailing on both the front and back enhances the overall craftsmanship, delivering a clean yet bold aesthetic. Finished with combed and bio-washed fabric, this tee ensures lasting softness, shape retention, and all-day wearability.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProducts in lighter shades (such as white or off-white) are \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"60\" data-end=\"99\"\u003enot eligible for return or exchange\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e due to the high risk of stains, discoloration, or signs of use during handling or trial. Customers are advised to review product details carefully before placing an order for these colors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Do not iron directly on embroidery. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium, heavyweight feel. Boxy fit for a relaxed and modern silhouette. Piping work across shoulders and front for elevated detailing. Front and back embroidery for a refined, high-quality finish. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Combed and bio-washed fabric for superior softness, durability, and long-lasting comfort.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":47079340507290,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079340540058,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079340572826,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079340605594,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079340638362,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":47079340671130,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00511copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440397"},{"product_id":"tempting","title":"TEMPTING","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Dual-Tone Colors. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Puff Print. Made for Club \u0026amp; House Parties.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is designed to blend soft aesthetics with bold, nightlife-ready detailing. Available in two refined shades—Baby Pink and Off-White—it delivers a clean yet statement-driven look. Crafted from premium French terry cotton, the fabric offers a smooth, substantial feel with breathable comfort and durability. Made specially for club and house parties, the front features a minimal printed logo for a refined finish, while the back stands out with a bold puff print reading \u003cstrong\u003e“AGAIN TEMPTED”\u003c\/strong\u003e alongside the signature \u003cstrong\u003e9\u003c\/strong\u003e, adding depth, texture, and standout appeal under lights. Combed and bio-washed for lasting softness, this tee is built for elevated after-dark wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve the puff print texture. Do not iron directly on the print. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium, heavyweight feel. Baby Pink and Off-White colorways crafted for night-out styling. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit ideal for club and house parties. Front logo print with bold “AGAIN TEMPTED” and 9 puff print on the back. High-quality puff printing for a textured, high-impact finish. Combed and bio-washed fabric for superior softness, durability, and shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079354466458,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079354499226,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079354531994,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47079354564762,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079354597530,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47079354630298,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1749.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00604copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440622"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. 100% French Terry Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Premium Puff \u0026amp; Screen Print. Exclusive Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM French terry cotton T-shirt is crafted to combine premium comfort with bold, statement-driven design. Built from heavyweight French terry cotton, the fabric delivers a smooth, structured feel while remaining breathable and durable for all-day wear. Designed as an exclusive limited-edition release, the front features the striking \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in a combination of premium puff and screen printing for layered texture and depth. The back carries the signature \u003cstrong\u003e09\u003c\/strong\u003e brand number in the same high-quality print finish, creating a cohesive, standout identity from every angle. Combed and bio-washed for long-lasting softness and shape retention, this tee is made for those who move with confidence and presence.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain print texture and fabric quality. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM French terry cotton for a premium heavyweight structure. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for everyday statement wear. Front “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” artwork in premium puff and screen print combination. Back brand number 09 executed in matching high-quality print finish. Exclusive limited-edition design for elevated street presence. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47500129829018,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47500129861786,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47500129894554,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47500129960090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47500129992858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687033159834,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00346copy_1__11zon.jpg?v=1772289837"},{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty-ii","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY II","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Heavyweight Fabric. High-Detail Puff Print Front \u0026amp; Back. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Exclusive YRM Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM premium T-shirt from the exclusive YRM limited-edition collection is designed to make a bold, unmistakable statement. Crafted from heavyweight fabric, it offers a structured yet breathable feel that delivers all-day comfort with a strong streetwear presence. The front and back feature intricately detailed \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in high-definition puff print, creating a striking raised texture that adds depth, dimension, and a premium visual impact. Designed for those who stand out effortlessly, this piece blends luxury aesthetics with everyday wearability. Combed and bio-washed for superior softness and long-lasting durability, it maintains its shape and finish over time while elevating your wardrobe with a powerful identity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric quality and puff print detailing. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM premium heavyweight fabric for a structured, high-end feel. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for statement streetwear. High-detail “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” puff print on both front and back for elevated texture and depth. Exclusive YRM limited-edition release for a distinctive look. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47682205384858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47682205417626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47682205450394,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47682205483162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47682205515930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687032373402,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00325_copy.webp?v=1774686690"}],"url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/collections\/dripcult-certified-heat.oembed","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}